Package: rkal
Type: Package
Title: Run, Import, and Export 'kallisto' Quantifications
Version: 0.1.12
Author: Alex Pickering
Maintainer: Alex Pickering <alexvpickering@gmail.com>
Description: Interface to 'kallisto' pseudo quantification utility. 'rkal' 
    automates running, importing, and exporting  'kallisto' quantification. This
    includes importing samples from ARCHS4 HDF5 data objects. Though general, 'rkal'
    is primarly intended for use by other packages e.g. crossmeta for differential
    expression and meta analyses.
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
SystemRequirements: kallisto
